data.title: The Origins of Contemporary France: The Modern Regime, vol. I
data.meta_description: The 1st volume of Hippolyte Taine’s 2 volume history of the Modern Regime which is part of his history of modern France, The Origins of Contemporary France. This volume deals with the state created by Napoleon and how it evolved during the 19th century.
data.text:
Hippolyte Taine (author)

John Durand (translator)

The 1st volume of Hippolyte Taine’s 2 volume history of the Modern Regime which is part of his history of modern France, The Origins of Contemporary France. This volume deals with the state created by Napoleon and how it evolved during the 19th century.
